  "texts": [
    "The content of this formula is presented in Eq.",
    "( 30) [60].Dice ¼ 2TP 2TP þ FP þ FNð30Þ2.",
    "Accuracy: The ratio of the number of correctly segmented pixels to the total number of pixels is represented by the accuracy expression [61].",
    "The accuracy formula is presented in Eq.",
    "(31).Accuracy ¼ TP þ TN TP þ TN þ FP þ FNð31Þ3."
  ]
}